Package com.ibm.di.protocols

Provides communication protocol classes for the Security Verify Directory Integrator.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    FTP
    This class implements the FTP functionality using a FTPClient object.
    FTPBean
    This class helps to expose the functionality of the FTP Client through the scripting environment.
    FTPBean.DirectoryContents
    This class is a container in which the contents of a directory can be saved.
    FTPClient
    This class represents a custom FTP client, that has the functionality to connect to a FTP server, to login, list contents, transfer data, etc.
    SNMP
    This class offers the functionality of the Simple Network Management.
